The couple then scheduled a meeting with Norwegian King Harald V and Queen Sonja.
In the afternoon, the visit reaches its climax with the ceremony, at which Obama takes over the prestigious award.
He is the fourth President of the United States, but only the third to receive the prize directly in office.
